{
  "stem": "10588.7",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "As long one vein is still-- as long the heart is beating, there is always hope.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Another expression that my father used a lot, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "A minute before 12:00 is not 12:00.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I use it now.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "A fact is not a fact 'til after the fact.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You know in Jewish, from the [NON-ENGLISH], you don't talk-- you don't make-- you can dream about the future.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You can plan of the future.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But you don't make a commitment about something you're going to do.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "For all you know, you might not be alive.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And it's there, where we were dying, that I learned the value of life and to live for now, and most of all, to be positive.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I remember distinctly, I was always a very spiritual person.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I realize that now.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I didn't know at the time that's called spirituality.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But I am a very intuitive person.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I trust my feelings and thoughts.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So sometimes, you know, intuition has nothing to do with logic.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So sometimes when I get a strong feeling to do or not to do something, it's not that I know I have a looking glass I can tell you what's going to be the future.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But just the heart tells me [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "There is a saying, 'The heart knows reason that reason doesn't know of.'",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when I get, then I follow it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And later, it turns out that it wasn't wrong.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So when I was in Auschwitz, one time I just had like a feeling, like I don't know what to call it, a vision, a feeling, that one day I'm going to be free.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they're going to stand people around the circle and everybody would want to see the number.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I laughed at myself.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
